On the rate scale where:
1-2 = Vid looks captured w/ a cell phone - mono sound
3-4 = VHS analog camera video - 'fuzzy' stereo sound
5-6 = High quality digital camera video - 2-channel stereo audio
7-8 = DVD rip video - clear stereo audio
9-10 = High-Def (720/1080) video - multi-channel surround sound audio

IMO currently the most reliable and consistent Inception torrent available.  Others may have better over-all quality but have periodic shaky & changing video/sound.
